2. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper talks about collecting and processing patient data, which involves information retrieval techniques. 
3. cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) - The paper mentions the real barriers in adopting IoT, which includes cybersecurity concerns. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses how IoT can be applied in healthcare, which involves social and information networks. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper mentions the enabling technologies required for IoT in healthcare, which involves software engineering.
